Text: Just met up with a friend in Rittenhouse and am heading home. Let me know if you’re up for a glass of vino tonight? If not tonight, definitely soon.
Just had an epic nap sorry! We leave for outer banks in the am and so much packing. Melissa works until 11pm. Yes! Soon please. After this the schedule cools down a bit. We are back next week

Hey we finally are leaving haha but we happened to have our handy man stop by and he just looked at our pipes and walls in bathrooms and no issues he can see. 

We are gone today - next Sunday so we won’t be around if something happens or if you need to get into our place.

We have a door code you can use to get in - 1985
Thanks…. Think it might be the condensation line in my place
We also have that. Especially now
But only little drips in our guest bathroom not the master bathroom
Just please only you entering we don’t want your landlord poking around haha
Lol… my landlord won’t even show up
I’ll keep you posted
Haha thank you so much Lauren!!!
No worries
Have fun in the OBX
☺️ thanks! Have a great weekend! Stay cool! It’s so hot today 🥵

Hi Lauren hope you’re having a good weekend! We are heading back and trying to get back into real life mode 😩 when you get a chance can you send Steven (maintenance man’s) phone number? I want to reach out to update him about our next steps with a plumber coming out to our unit this week to repair the toilet. Thank you so much!
Thank you so much!
No problem
Is it still leaking?
Your plumber is likely going to have to access a crawl space under your bathroom
No it’s not leaking that we know of but the plumber wants to come back Tuesday to repair and we wanted to let Steven know so he has a heads up! And we left VM for Karen too!
How’s your place? Still water?

Just keeping you on the loop. Your landlord texted me and said he arrived today and there was no longer a leak so that’s good news. The plumber arrives tomorrow between 8-9am. Not sure if it’s going to be the same guy or not. Either way, I will be here and I don’t see a need to have them in your place. I’m about to ask Steve the maintenance guy to be here with me. Our handy man can’t make it but will join by phone to help the cause

Hi there guys! Let me know if you are around tonight or tomorrow and would like to come down for some vino?!

Come on up around 9 ? We are getting dinner soon and then playing some games around 9

sorry something just popped up and can we reschedule ? Sorry about this
Sure… no problem

My folks are coming into town on Thursday for Easter weekend… no worries if you are using it, as I can always park one of my cars on the street or in a paid garage, but figured I’d ask. I want to try to comply with the new parking requirements. 🤷‍♀️

Hey, I will take what I can get. Thank you, that would be awesome!
Ok wanna get it Saturday morning from parking lot? Say 9am?
Sure. I can have my parents go out to grab it. I am actually going to be heading out between 8-10 that morning for a quick appointment.
I can meet you at 8
